                Mr. Hudson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f8e938b8-c6c2-43b5-b59e-baab878f3170" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
