<p class="">There is a great desire to hear about them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6899fa9d-8893-491b-b9c2-b5b5938ceec1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1945-10-17/debates/d9a4610d-1861-45b9-b667-1a737bfdc21f/HousingShortage#contribution-6899fa9d-8893-491b-b9c2-b5b5938ceec1">
