                Major Guy Lloyd  (Renfrew, Eastern)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c3b61ce7-7c4e-401c-a00a-32e79bfc60dc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
